  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is being conducted to assess the safety and tolerability of an oral liquid
      solution of Sustiva for antiretroviral therapy-naive or therapy-experienced HIV-1 infected
      children between the ages of 3-16 who are failing or intolerant of their current
      antiretroviral regimen and who are unable to swallow Sustiva capsules.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
